00:02:55.864 --> 00:03:08.546
This is whenever you're seeing in part and hearing in part, and whenever there's a depth perception in the spirit realm.

00:03:08.546 --> 00:03:29.840
I warned you all about the Red Dawn; I told you there are people within our government that are not good, who have been hired as spies.

00:03:43.051 --> 00:04:01.774
I'm trying to be discreet, but I'm just saying there are things we need to pray about on our YouTube prayer channel here to take our authority and keep protecting President Trump and his family.

00:04:01.774 --> 00:04:25.499
Now he says he's going to the Super Bowl, and I told everybody, 'Watch the Super Bowl.

00:04:25.499 --> 00:04:51.429
' I've had a check about the Super Bowl, but it hasn't been very intense as of the last two days.

00:04:55.976 --> 00:05:19.303
It was intense about a week ago, and I was talking to somebody on the phone who asked what I was praying about.

00:05:19.303 --> 00:05:24.000
I said the Super Bowl.

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:42.900
I don't understand why, but it's about the Super Bowl again, so I'm interceding for the Super Bowl.

00:05:55.148 --> 00:05:55.445
They said they were feeling something about it too.

00:05:59.617 --> 00:06:13.348
Like I said, it's not as intense, and I know I'm talking fast because I have a lot to say.

00:06:13.348 --> 00:06:32.155
You'll see this in this video: when the spirit of the Lord comes on me, I feel pulses.

00:06:32.155 --> 00:06:51.160
It's an intensity of how serious of a timeframe we're looking at and how imminent it is.

00:06:58.840 --> 00:07:10.039
The more I feel that urgency, I pray into it in tongues and I just ask the Lord to give me more sight to see into it.

00:07:10.039 --> 00:07:32.700
If I need to know anything, warn me of things to come; that's what I do as a watchman on the wall.

00:07:32.700 --> 00:08:33.936
What you're about to see are things that I have been praying over for the last six months or so about Israel, the Jonathan relationship, and praying over the Strait—the passageway where all the oil tankers come through—and praying over strategic strikes against Iran to make them where they don't have nuclear capabilities.

00:08:33.936 --> 00:08:44.200
Thank you for watching this; I hope this blesses you all.

00:08:44.200 --> 00:09:01.760
Right after that, I'm going to tell you all about the Dinar and what the Lord has showed me.

00:09:08.440 --> 00:09:53.263
I saw in the land of prophecies, Israel, and in that sea where Israel owns a massive reservoir of oil and natural gas that will be tapped into; it's worth billions and billions over the next four years.

00:09:53.263 --> 00:10:02.103
Great financial wealth will flow through Israel.

00:10:13.320 --> 00:10:18.564
I saw their agriculture; I saw fruit the size of, like, ginormous.

00:10:18.564 --> 00:10:49.860
I don't know if they're oranges—I don't even know if they grow oranges, folks—but I saw fruit that was ginormous and vegetables that were beautiful and healthy.

00:10:50.440 --> 00:11:15.942
The Lord said it's the Abrahamic Covenant, a supernatural breathing on it, an evidence showing that God is God over Israel.

00:11:20.583 --> 00:11:38.548
It will come through blessing, favor, and wealth as America backs it, and favor and blessing and wealth come on America.

00:11:41.668 --> 00:11:53.213
I saw the founding fathers making a covenant with the Father.

00:11:53.213 --> 00:12:24.510
There were two sides of the covenant: this side was their side of promises where they would make their allegiance to the Father, and the Father's side was His side to a man.

00:12:31.671 --> 00:12:39.200
It was great and strong on the Father's side because He's always held up His agreement.

00:12:39.200 --> 00:12:57.265
It was strong like a tie in the spirit realm, and I could see it through time.

00:12:57.265 --> 00:13:14.465
I could see George Washington and all the great men—the pilgrims at Plymouth Rock—making that covenant with the Father.

00:13:14.465 --> 00:13:31.120
It looked like blood, a blood covenant, with strands of muscle and tissue that made it bound together.

00:13:31.550 --> 00:13:45.755
The Father's side was strong and has never altered, but we have entered into compromise.

00:13:45.755 --> 00:14:16.240
There were barely even just a few threads left before that covenant was broken—basically a breach of contract because we did not hold up our end of the agreement.

00:14:21.302 --> 00:14:23.213
But the Father's side was completely strong.

00:14:23.213 --> 00:14:40.564
I saw as Donald Trump made an alliance with Israel, it saved the contract because it blessed Israel.

00:14:40.564 --> 00:15:10.826
As the covenant made with us in America was getting weaker, God had every right to cut it completely, but He is rich in mercy.

00:15:10.826 --> 00:15:39.655
When Donald Trump comes in, I saw him bridge the gap of the covenant of our founding fathers to make it strong by blessing Israel.

00:15:39.655 --> 00:16:31.480
We did not hold our agreement to be one nation under God like we should have; we've let compromise in and done things that have been ungodly with all kinds of parties, Republican and Democrat.

00:16:41.679 --> 00:16:41.979
It has been several decades of faulty leadership.

00:16:41.979 --> 00:17:12.380
It's like a third layer grew on top, and it was a golden glowing thread as we bless Israel that made us have a lifeline over America.

00:17:12.380 --> 00:17:27.445
Because it's a three-strand cord, it made it a strong covenant again.

00:17:27.445 --> 00:17:40.271
It's like a Jonathan and David relationship about to happen with Israel and America.

00:17:49.560 --> 00:18:03.337
This is going to be a different relationship than we've ever seen before between Benjamin Netanyahu and Donald Trump.

00:18:03.337 --> 00:18:43.506
The moment Trump is inaugurated on the 20th, I saw him come out like a lion and I saw strategic plans of taking out key select targets in the Middle East within a small span of time.

00:18:56.451 --> 00:18:58.105
I'm talking about using the military like a chess game, and I saw Iran crippled financially.

00:18:58.105 --> 00:19:11.652
A great setback is coming to Iran regarding their nuclear capabilities and technology.

00:19:11.652 --> 00:19:29.493
I saw weapons that the United States has never used before in battle being used against foreign adversaries.

00:19:47.300 --> 00:20:04.594
I saw a heavy military presence—aircraft carriers and battleships—in the Mediterranean and around the oceans there as an intimidation like you've never seen before in that Strait where they're always picking on those ships.

00:20:04.594 --> 00:20:23.060
The respect that America has lost with our foreign adversaries over the last four years is going to be restored.

00:20:23.060 --> 00:20:42.620
We have been the laughingstock of the world, but when he comes in, respect will be restored back to America.

00:20:42.620 --> 00:20:57.240
It's a type and shadow of Ronald Reagan coming back into power, but even stronger.

00:20:57.240 --> 00:21:05.200
People are going to take America serious again.

00:21:05.200 --> 00:21:41.651
We are going to have to pray for protection around him, but a major bulldog is coming on the scene, more aggressive than he was his first four years.

00:21:41.651 --> 00:21:52.440
I saw him hitting strategic targets in Iran and Syria.

00:21:52.440 --> 00:22:04.342
It's going to look like shock and awe.

00:22:04.342 --> 00:22:20.279
I saw a cracking of a whip over the Middle East and strategic alliances being formed.

00:22:26.416 --> 00:22:31.420
It is like a sign in a window saying, 'We're back in business.

00:22:31.420 --> 00:22:47.431
' I'm talking drill baby drill—you're going to see oil like you've never seen it before.

00:22:47.431 --> 00:23:05.340
You're going to see pipelines being established and people who were laid off getting their jobs back.

00:23:05.340 --> 00:23:16.064
It's about putting America first and a return of patriotism.

00:23:16.064 --> 00:23:48.559
When I was praying, the Lord showed me that the Third Temple is about to be built and that Trump will have a major part in bringing forth the peace accord with Saudi Arabia and other nations.

00:23:48.559 --> 00:23:54.845
Well, good morning family.

00:24:05.719 --> 00:24:10.405
